What is Load Balancer ?

It is used to route the traffic into multiple targets such as EC2 instances.


Types:-

Classic Load Balancer: It operates transport layer.
Application Load Balancer: It operates application layer and provide path based routing.
Network Load Balancer: It operates transport layer and used for high-performance/high workloads.
Gateway Load Balancer: It operates network layer and used for third party virtual appliances.
